The '''Azaria 66''' was a product created by [[Alkherrodyne Propulsions]], with [[Klaus Vandangante/Legends|Klaus "Doc" Vandangante]] as design systems team leader. Though Vandangante was conscientious, Alkherrodyne in general was rife with shoddy workmanship, covered with flashy marketing, and the Azaria 66 was no exception.<ref name="Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook">''[[Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook]]''</ref> Vandangante warned the company that the product wasn't safe, but they released it, anyway.<ref name="Databank">{{DB|character|doc|Doc}}</ref> When it began exploding in minor accidents, Alkherrodyne's [[Slicer/Legends|slicers]] framed Doc. The countless lawsuits wiped out the Vandangante family fortune, and left his name slandered.<ref name="Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook" />

